Package: bmp
Maintainer: Gregory Jefferis <jefferis@gmail.com>
License: GPL (>=2)
Title: Read Windows Bitmap (BMP) Images
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "Gregory",
           family = "Jefferis",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jefferis@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0587-9355"))
